    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Salvia karelinii are anxiety, depression and insomnia, which are alleviated by its neuroprotective and adaptogenic properties, reducing oxidative stress and inflammation in the brain. Salvia karelinii's anti-inflammatory compounds also address inflammation, pain, migraines and stress, as well as hypertension, which is further reduced by its vasodilatory effects. Digestive issues, such as arthritis, asthma and chronic pain, are alleviated by its antimicrobial and anti-inflammatory actions, while diabetes is managed through its antioxidant and insulin-sensitizing properties. Additionally, bronchitis and fever are treated with its expectorant and antipyretic properties, and infections are combated by its antimicrobial and immunomodulatory effects. Menstrual cramps and cancer are also alleviated by its anti-inflammatory and antioxidant compounds, including salvinorin A, a potent inhibitor of cancer cell growth.",
